(163, 35, '\"Email Testing \"', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #134f5c; font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\"><strong>শ্রদ্ধেয় স্যার</strong></span><strong style=\"color: #134f5c; font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">,</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">আসসালামু আলাইকুম</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #e69138;\">এস্টিম সফট লিমিটেড</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">-এর পক্ষ থেকে জানাই স্বাগতম।</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">আশা করছি&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">\"কোভিড-১৯\"</span></strong>&nbsp;মহামারিকালীন সময়ে&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">সুস্থ</span>&nbsp;</strong>এবং&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><strong>নিরাপদ</strong></span>&nbsp;আছেন।</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">আপনার নিকট&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">National&nbsp;</span>ICT&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">Award</span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">2019</span></strong><span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">&nbsp;</span><wbr />বিজয়ী হাসপাতাল ব্যবস্থাপনা সফটওয়্যার&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">আর্চ</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">(Arch)</span></strong>&nbsp;উপস্থাপন করতে পেরে আমরা আনন্দিত।&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">আর্চ</span><span style=\"color: #6fa8dc;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">(Arch)</span>&nbsp;</strong>হাসপাতাল ব্যবস্থাপনা সফটওয়্যার একটি&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><strong>অত্যাধুনিক</strong></span>&nbsp;<strong style=\"color: #38761d;\">ও</strong>&nbsp;<strong style=\"color: #38761d;\">উন্নত মানের</strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"BN-BD\" style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">সফটওয়্যার</span></span><strong><span lang=\"BN-BD\" style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span lang=\"BN-BD\" style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">যা যেকোনো&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\"><strong>হাসপাতাল</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;<span lang=\"BN-BD\"><strong><span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">ক্লিনিক&nbsp;</span></strong>এবং&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\"><strong>ডা<wbr />য়াগনস্টিক সেন্টার</strong></span></span>&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">-&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">এর</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong>কার্যক্রমকে&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">করবে&nbsp;<wbr />সহজ, সময় সাশ্রয়ী এবং স্মার্ট।&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">এটি একটি&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #45818e;\">ওয়েব ভিত্তিক অনলাইন</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;সফটওয়্যার যা&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #45818e;\">বিশ্বের যেকোনো প্রান্ত</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;থেকে সহজেই এবং দ্রুতগতিতে ব্যবহার করা যায়।&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: small; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; line-height: 22px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Nirmala UI\', sans-serif;\">আমাদের সফটওয়্যার-এর&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">মডিউল</span></strong>&nbsp;ও&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #3d85c6;\">সুবিধা</span>&nbsp;</strong>সমূ<wbr />হ